# =============================================================================
# DOMOVINA-API — Coolify env "extra/secret" layer (template)
#
# Kopiraj u .coolify-extra.env (gitignored) i popuni vrijednostima. Ovo je
# OPCIONALNI treći sloj koji coolify-env-merge.sh nanosi PREKO live dumpa +
# coolify-config-overrides.env. Najjači prioritet (EXTRA > overrides > live).
#
# Namjena: ne-tajni config koji NE ide u committed override (jer ovisi o okolini)
# I secreti koje treba dodati u Coolify env (npr. KYC_ENCRYPTION_KEY). Vrijednosti
# odavde su u merge diffu MASKIRANE i nikad se ne ispisuju u chat.
#
# Workflow:
#   cp .coolify-extra.env.example .coolify-extra.env
#   # popuni vrijednosti
#   ./scripts/coolify-env-merge.sh      # bundle u clipboard + .coolify-merged.env
#   # Coolify Bulk edit → Paste → Save → Deploy
# =============================================================================

# --- certilia edge function (eID KYC bridge) ---------------------------------
# CERTILIA_CLIENT_ID  — OIDC client ID (audience za idToken verify). Nije pravi
#                       secret, ali ovisi o Certilia okruženju (prod/test).
# KYC_ENCRYPTION_KEY  — SECRET. pgcrypto ključ za enkripciju OIB-a u
#                       public.identity_verifications. Generiraj jakim randomom,
#                       čuvaj samo ovdje + u Coolifyju, NIKAD u repo/chat.
# CERTILIA_ISSUER     — opcionalno; code default je https://idp.certilia.com.
CERTILIA_CLIENT_ID=
KYC_ENCRYPTION_KEY=
# CERTILIA_ISSUER=https://idp.certilia.com
